{"author":{"id":"b78c39e7b13f90a5827abfba043255fe7a4ede1499df23f110fffe5abfa44adc"},"ops":[{"type":6,"timestamp":1769467794,"nonce":"ZDNr2QmkdpDX5pxoP9ysQGsbOcQ=","metadata":{"github-id":"UCE_lAHOQ241x87l9DiYzp9AINc"},"target":"b11fcb04eb0e5b413a1081620ede71aa85c885807ba90e65fcf4d6f149241c8b","message":"## Description\nIt has been observed that agents are occasionally creating temporary files within package source directories and failing to clean them up. Subsequently, other agents are mistakenly committing these files to the repository.\n\n## Relevant Documentation\n- **.agent/rules/common/clean-root.md**: Currently suggests `./ai_workspace` or `/tmp`.\n- **AGENTS.md**: explicitly advises against modifying `workspaces/*/src/` unless instructed.\n\n## Proposed Solutions\n1. **Standardize on `.agent/scratchpad/`**: Deprecate `ai_workspace/` in favor of a hidden, dedicated directory inside `.agent/`. This keeps the root clean and groups agent artifacts logically.\n2. **Update `.gitignore`**: Ensure `.agent/scratchpad/` is ignored, along with common temp patterns.\n3. **Refine Agent Rules**: Update `clean-root.md` to mandate `.agent/scratchpad/` for persistent temp files.\n4. **Pre-commit Checks**: Implement a check to warn about untracked files in source directories.","files":null},{"type":3,"timestamp":1769480143,"nonce":"luLCc+B8aOjuUXxzrOau4GtE74Q=","metadata":{"github-id":"IC_kwDOQ241x87iqKQB","github-url":"https://github.com/rolker/ros2_agent_workspace/issues/44#issuecomment-3802702849"},"message":"Closing as fixed by merged PR #47.","files":null},{"type":4,"timestamp":1769480143,"nonce":"M+XZaMPkGCFYWiefSysl6XaIFcY=","metadata":{"github-id":"CE_lADOQ241x87l9DiYzwAAAAUxetEd"},"status":2}]}